      for me when i inevitably look back on this project","body":"so what''s happening
      is that you initially tried to grab the reference to the object, remove the
      reference to that object in the list, and then destroy that object. Doesn''t
      work, you need to destroy all items in the list first, and then remove the
      (now) missing references to the items.","colorTheme":"Classic","guid":"f8756b27-7e07-413a-865c-ea8d551eb5d8","$type":"Unity.VisualScripting.StickyNote"},{"position":{"xMin":3600.0,"yMin":17.0,"xMax":3883.0,"yMax":117.0},"title":"note","body":"if
